Author: livipup
Text: If you want to be thinner maybe you can achieve that by just maintaining the same weight and building muscles in places you're okay with? It would be better to be lean and strong than be soft and weak. You could be reasonably thin still while being strong. Plenty of people manage it.

Author: goldenlttuce
Text: Stay calm, I'm sure you're strong and have the power to overcome any obstacle in your way ‚ù§ I'm here if you need to talk.
